com.day.cq.wcm.api.msm

Interface LiveAction

  • Deprecated. 
    since 5.3 use com.day.cq.wcm.msm.api.LiveAction instead

    @Deprecated
public interface LiveAction
    Represent an rollout action. Action is executed by RolloutManager through the ActionManager.
    See Also:
    RolloutManager, ActionManager
